high_descs: Turn around, move to the towel on the wall.
Pick up the towel on the wall.
Turn around, bring the towel to the toilet.
Place the towel on the toilet tank lid.
Turn right, head to the tub, turn right, go to the towel on the wall, left of the sink.
Pick up the towel on the wall.
Turn around, head back to the toilet on the left.
Put the towel on the toilet tank lid, right of the other towel.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: Turn around and go to towel holder on the wall next to the mirror.
Remove the towel from the holder.
Turn around and go to the toilet in the left corner.
Place the towel on the toilet tank on the right of the candle.
Turn around and go to the towel holder on the opposite side next to the bath tub.
Remove the towel from the holder.
Turn around and go back to the toilet in the left corner.
Place the towel on the top of the tank on right of the first towel.
anns.task_desc: Move two towels to the top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn to the left.
Take the towel off the holder.
Turn around to the right. Face the toilet.
Place the towel on the back end of the toilet.
Turn and go to the right. Make another right at the tub.
Take the other towel off the holder.
Turn around and go to the left. Then turn right and go back to the toilet.
Place the towel on the back end of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two towels to the back end of the toilet.
